SQL> 
SQL> REM TYPES FUNCTIONS : 1 CHARACTER 2 NUMBER 3 DATE : CHAPTER 3
SQL> 
SQL> REM TYPES FUNCTIONS : 4 CONVERSION 5 GENERAL : CHAPTER 4
SQL> 
SQL> REM TYPES OF GENERAL FUNCTIONS : 1 NULL RELATED FUNCTIONS 2 CONDITIONAL FUNCTIONS
SQL> 
SQL> REM LIST OF NULL RELATED FUNCTIONS : 1 NVL 2 NVL2 3 NULLIF 4 COALESCE
SQL> 
SQL> REM NVL : IS USED TO REPLACE NULL VALUE WITH OTHER VALUE
SQL> 
SQL> REM IT ACCEPTS TWO ARGUMENTS.
SQL> 
SQL> REM BOTH ARGUMENTS ARE MANDATORY.
SQL> 
SQL> REM DATA TYPES OF BOTH ARGUMENTS MUST MATCH.
SQL> 
SQL> REM COMPANY DECIDES TO PAY .12 COMMISSION TO THOSE WHO DOESN'T GET COMMISSION.
