SQL> REM NVL2 : IT TAKES 3 ARGUMENTS.
SQL> 
SQL> REM ALL 3 ARGUMENTS ARE MANDATORY.
SQL> 
SQL> REM IT WILL CHECK FIRST ARGUMENT. IF IT IS NULL IT WILL BE REPLACED WITH THIRD ARGUMENT. IF IT IS NOT NULL, IT WILL BE REPLACED BY SECOND ARGUMENT.
SQL> 
SQL> REM DATA TYPES OF 2ND AND 3RD ARGUMENT MUST MATCH OR DATA TYPE OF 2ND ARGUMENT MUST BE CHARACTER TYPE.
SQL> 
SQL> REM COMPANY DECIDES TO PAY .12 TO THOSE WHO DOESN'T GET COMMISSION AND .25 TO THOSE WHO GETS COMMISSION.
SQL> 
